  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if an ostomy barrier that promotes a healthy skin
      environment will result in reduced peristomal skin irritation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
